title: Dove of The East Europe Journey Bag of Chips Self-Adhesive Chipboard Stickers
features: A variety of over 18 different die-cut shapes and designs
No plastic packaging to discard - use the cardboard backer, gold and red elastic and reusable drawstring organza pouch in your projects
We love our stickers and hope you will enjoy these culturally specific yet universal designs
description: Welcome to Europe Journey Bag of Chips - Foreign Accents by Dove of the East- an organza bag filled with color-printed, die-cut, self-adhesive chipboard stickers. Classic, opulent and elegant, Europe Journey travels back in time to imperial Europe when empires were ruled by Kings and Tzars, Queens and Tzarinas. From the mystical forests to the grand palaces, Dove of the East chipboard stickers let you create the magic of imperial Europe with your own imagination. Enjoy Europe Journey stickers in your scrapbooking, stamping, card making, altered books, crafts and other artistic projects. You get 30 die-cut, self-adhesive chipboard stickers with peel-off backing in a reusable drawstring organza pouch. These include birds, flowers, berries, decorative corners, faux filigree, tiny frames, horse and carriage, trumpeting angels and more. Put a little Foreign Accent on your invitations, stationery, craft projects and scrapbook pages for a touch of elegance. Enjoy the Journey! Let your imagination take flight!
